{
  "stem": "9723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he came, uh, and warned, uh, my father that this was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, uh, when it got dark, we, we walked out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Before this, before this incident, we tried to get out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and, uh, we knew that this was come sooner or later, that, uh, it was no secret that the ghetto was going to be liquidated.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, uh, my parents tried to find a place to, uh, to hide.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For some time before, I think that was before even before we moved into this medical residence building, we spent some times with some patients of my father's outside of town.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Polish patients?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, I'm not sure were they Polish, or Czech, or Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Perhaps they were Czech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we stayed in their house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The son of these people was very sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was just recently married, had a small baby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was not expected to survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I don't know whether he had cancer or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I guess they felt they let us stay, because that way, father could be next, close to him all the time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after several days or a week, uh, the man died.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a big wake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I still remember, uh, his father, uh, was making a speech.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he says, well, the doctor, even though he was a Jew, he did the best he could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we're not blaming him for anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after this, I guess my father felt that it was not a good idea to stay there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we moved into this medical, uh, house.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
